Title:
Login error message is not specific

Description:
When the user enters incorrect credentials, the system displays a generic error message that does not indicate which field is incorrect.

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Go to login page
2. Enter invalid username
3. Enter valid password
4. Click Login button

Expected Result:
System should indicate whether the username or password is incorrect.

Actual Result:
System displays generic error message without specifying the incorrect field.

Severity:
Low